content: I signed up for Discord but the downloaded app isn't loading. Just get a blank black screen. However the web app is working. Help?
Maybe try deleting the app and re-downloading it again?
Hi Brad, I want to help you have a better experience. Let's try to turn your phone off and back on again. If that doesn't fix it, can you share what phone OS you are using?
Sorry this is on my mac laptop. Is the downloadable app only for iPhones?

Sorry I misunderstood. down load the laptop app from 
https://discord.com/download and make sure you are on macOS 10.15 (Catalina) or higher
Thanks, downloaded for the third time and finally got it to open.  Third time's a charm! Thanks for your help.
